{"tid":835712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【封殺港獨】不因政治打壓退縮 獨立聯盟陳家駒高呼：港獨無錯！","createTime":"2018-09-25T06:22:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T10:03:57.000Z","uid":47359,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"79c813abc2d757725233cc1baa180596a6322ec8","tid":835712,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:22:18.000Z","msg":"【封殺港獨】不因政治打壓退縮 獨立聯盟陳家駒高呼：港獨無錯！<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180925&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58721013\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180925%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58721013&d=Mp8yynpZk4R88lIBgfKdKviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e5029d5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180925%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58721013&h=8cdbcc0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180925&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58721013</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/142044_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F142044_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ba61c3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/142046_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F142046_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b13fe4bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府昨日刊憲以《社團條例》禁止主張港獨的香港民族黨運作，社民連、人民力量、立法會議員毛孟靜等約30人今早在警總外示威，抗議當局以言入罪，剝奪結社自由。學生獨立聯盟召集人陳家駒聯同數名支持者出席行動，他們高舉「香港獨立」旗幟和標語，並明言「民族自強、香港獨立無錯」，會堅持港獨立場。<br />\n<br />\n陳家駒發言時指，香港民族黨只是主張民族自強、香港擁有海水化淡廠、香港有獨立的貨幣、經濟獨立減少依賴中國等，他認為以上主張都只希望香港民族自強，是「無罪嘅」，但卻被政府誣蔑成為非法政黨。他指，香港政府取締民族黨非常不智，亦顯示了中共用壓力打壓異見聲音，擔心香港政府日後會以支持民族黨為由，打壓認為不可信的人，強調「民族自強無錯、香港獨立無錯」，不會因為政治打壓而退縮，並指學生獨立聯盟會繼續堅持香港獨立，並與支持者高叫「香港獨立，以死相搏」口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n社民連前議員梁國雄其後向傳媒表示，暫時未與陳浩天有聯絡，他形容《社團條例》惡毒，令陳浩天由昨日開始不能以民族黨身份發言，否則犯法，故令陳浩天不能透露下一步行動。他指，民主派可以做的是抗議政府剝奪結社自由，強調結社自由是文明社會的基石，是香港人不能再讓的底線，故他們不會擔心因而受牽連。他又指，特首林鄭月娥和律政司司長鄭若驊有責任向市民解釋，會否因為支持民族黨而誤墮法網。"},{"pid":"45cda7cd1007ab8d32b7cb9f56bbc7eb2fb31b62","tid":835712,"uid":133680,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:26:17.000Z","msg":"又借死人上位諗住呃九萬六，cheap唔cheap d？"},{"pid":"cc1c415728c69d19edfef8f8b662843d1e1760a0","tid":835712,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:41:06.000Z","msg":"加油！ <br />\n<br />\n請問有乜途經可以資助 / 支持學獨聯?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lihkg.com/assets/faces/mf/special2.gif\" />"},{"pid":"0ed6d540eaa53a31e228ec640d58ac6882595d15","tid":835712,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ccc57547dc479dddb56609a4bf0985e1cba491","tid":835712,"uid":131084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:46:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd2ae7f21167f8682194e7640fe65a8794a1f4aa","tid":835712,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549199ff8d7deb8c3e0a4a9dfabf12faef7415a3","tid":835712,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5b1abd7a1eb61f845eb497b48cd7f4b72c16f3","tid":835712,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94300aa5353654315e9a34721a58e55062796e14","tid":835712,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc1c415728c69d19edfef8f8b662843d1e1760a0","tid":835712,"uid":79563,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T06:4